#

Smoky Corn Guacamole

10 min
$5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerDipSnack

Description

A creamy, smoky twist on traditional guacamole, enhanced with sweet roasted corn kernels and a hint of smoked paprika.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • roasted corn kernels: 1 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • red onion, diced: 1/4 cup
  • cilantro, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • smoked paprika: 1/2 teaspoon
